Zero point energy                ...      0.15620910 Eh      98.02 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.01652100 Eh      10.37 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
